Tatum is 21

21

Seriously

How can this not be talked about more often??

A couple years ago, the hype was a little too high too early

But

They were right

This dude could be one of the top 3 players in the game in 6/7 years

When he’s 27 lol

At 21, he’s taken it to kawhi 2 times in the same season and dropped 30 spots on his head.

Broken PGs ankles and hit a game tying step back 2.

Throwing down poster dunks left and right

This dude is 21. Why does the media not want to talk about Boston unless it’s bad news??

Shut up about ohilly. You’ve been on them for 3/4 years now and they aren’t even close to expectations. Let it go

Talk abut the team that no one other than max saw coming this year

The team that people hated on for a few days after they lost kyire( who they didn’t want to keep..). Segments about how Danny Ainge actuallt hasn’t ever done anything good and is overrated as a GM. Nick wriggt invladiated any moves he has made and made excuses for why Danny really hasn’t done anything, he just “got lucky” once with Kg and ray.
Then?
A week later?
Danny had AGaIN rebuilt a team that can compete for titles in a week.

Idiots.

Danny is a genius. The celtics are so good RN

They are going to be even better.

Jaylen is 23
Tatum is 21
Smart is 25
Tons of picks and assets.

38-16 record.

No love.

Wow. Ftfoh.
Also, how isnt brown an all star lol?? 20 a game on 50 percent FG for a 2 guard? Making 2/3 3s a game on 37/38 percent as well. Playing great D. Clutch plays. Uber consistent.

Maybe it’s about how the media and fans across the country can’t get over how jealous they are of NE area fans. Getting like, Idk, 11/12 CHAMPIONSHIPs in the last 20 years lol. Jealousy ain’t a good look. And the more they ignore it, the more they are gonna get proved wrong and give the celtics more to play for lol.

Tatum just dropped 39 on kawahi. On 55 percent shooting

He’s 21
2.1.
Wtf
